{"tid":2361151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王浩信北上工作回港唔使隔離 今晚現身台慶頒獎禮","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T14:28:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"755be67462079a422d4d70d3255dbe1adf9e4077","tid":2361151,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"有指無綫為了讓王浩信再登視帝寶座，於是抽起陳展鵬主演的劇集《唐人街》。早前浩信北上開工，日前他在社交平台表示已完成兩個多月的工作，馬上就回港拉票和準備出席頒獎典禮，今日更留言道︰「感恩這一切，今晚見！」<br />\n<br />\n政府早前宣布「回港易」計劃，豁免香港居民從廣東省或澳門回港檢疫安排。浩信日前返港，又不用隔離便可出席頒獎禮，相信他便是透過這個計劃申請回港。"},{"pid":"59cf611909ccd1856aba4d9d29d865723ef3596d","tid":2361151,"uid":224533,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"頒獎典禮群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ee086b04e8e5548232f4676d4a6f92b242195b","tid":2361151,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"我又諗起你老婆喇.jpg"},{"pid":"e8c230c810d77913e5ed8491911971f5df0d35de","tid":2361151,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />群組"},{"pid":"6a6a07bc34f8f5897a4b9c1c5dc21cbf93cede6e","tid":2361151,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ee086b04e8e5548232f4676d4a6f92b242195b","tid":2361151,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"我又諗起你老婆喇.jpg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"喂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4307a7b9d26f8ea494ec74c81e483fb227e239c0","tid":2361151,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a6a07bc34f8f5897a4b9c1c5dc21cbf93cede6e","tid":2361151,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ee086b04e8e5548232f4676d4a6f92b242195b","tid":2361151,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-1